body_text:
Disabling IOMMU temporarily resolves this issue.
I am still wondering though, as it seems distributed runtime triggers GPU P2P transfer even with CPU as local PS, but the same error does not occur in local training. Is this behaviour intended?
@poxvoculi Paul, is there anything you feel familiar here?

